      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Relief/Estate of M.N./Broward County Sheriff's Office;  Provides for an appropriation to compensate estate for injuries sustained by M.N. & her subsequent death as result of negligence of Broward County Sheriff's Office; provides limitation on compensation & payment of attorney fees.\r\n    \r\n        CLAIM:\r\n        $2,588,259"
    }
